  "Description": {
    "English": "A map of a nearby planet. An ancient ruined site has been marked. Excavating this site is likely to yield <span class=\"name name-special\">valuable treasures</span>.<br><br>Select the map and use <VAL_ON>Plot Route (<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>)<> to pin the location in your Exosuit display.<br><br>New maps can be gained by exchanging <span class=\"name name-commodity\">Navigation Data</span> with a Space Station Cartographer.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一张附近行星的地图，现已标记一处<span class=\"name name-special\">远古废墟地点</span>。在此地进行挖掘很有可能会得到宝藏。<br><br>选择地图并使用<VAL_ON>规划路线（<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>）<>以在你的套装屏幕中标记该地点。<br><br>与空间站制图师交换<span class=\"name name-commodity\">导航数据</span>以获取新的地图。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "附近行星的地圖，已標記一處古老遺址地點。到現場挖掘就有機會找到<span class=\"name name-special\">珍貴的寶藏</span>。<br><br>選取地圖後，使用<VAL_ON>規劃路線功能 (<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>)<> 即可在你的強化套裝顯示器中釘選該地點。<br><br>與太空站地圖學家交換<span class=\"name name-commodity\">導航資料</span>，即可獲得新星系圖。"
  },
